  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dc3\u0d9a \u0daf\u0db8\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0db1\u0db8 \u0d85\u0dad\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The principal put the cane on the ground and took the steering wheel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The principal of Sirimavo Bandaranaike Primary School in Medirigiriya is transporting his school children who have difficulty in transporting them to school by school bus.",
        "The principal who did not take action to close schools island wide due to the fuel crisis has taken action to transport a large number of children with transportation difficulties by school bus back home after school hours.",
        "The principal arrives at the school by bicycle at 6.30 am and takes action to bring children to school in the Medirigiriya, Navanagaraya, Chaityapara, Diyasenpura, 5 Ela, Parakumpura, Track 9 and Wijayarajapura areas where the school is located.",
        "The principal said that he would carry out this task continuously for about three weeks and that the parents would bring the required fuel to the school as much as possible.",
        "The principal has used his school opening time of 8.00 am as a solution to the transportation problem when the education of the children was disrupted due to the fuel crisis. Accordingly, the school bus will ply in a large area under 3 trips.",
        "The school will close at 1.30 pm and the principal will take all the children home safely by 2.30 pm.",
        "The parents have informed the principal at the school development society about the difficulties they have in bringing their children to school and the principal has taken this decision."
      ],
